data.description: Beautiful Classic built stucco rancher with a full basement located in Banning Lewis Ranch!  This home offers 4 bedrooms, office, 3 bathrooms and a 2 car garage. The main floor offers true Single Floor Living-(Master Suite, Kitchen, Laundry, Great Room, Guest Full Bath, Guest Bedroom and Office).  Entry, great room, and kitchen flows nicely with grey engineered hardwood throughout.  Spacious open kitchen displays 42" white cabinets, solid quartz countertops, composite sink, large kitchen island, pantry, newer stainless-steel appliances, stove area is plumbed with natural gas, adjacent to great-room and walk-out to rear concrete patio with a privacy wall and hot tub. Master suite offers a large bedroom with lots of windows, quartz countertops with dual sinks, walk-in  shower and large walk-in closet. Majority finished basement has two large guest bedrooms, full bathroom, large unfinished storage room that is plumbed for an additional bathroom, utility room with high efficient furnace and hot water heater, humidifier and central air conditioning, and a super spacious family room.  The entire lot is nicely Xeriscaped with an automatic sprinkler/drip system. Sizeable two car garage with automatic garage door opener, door leading to side/back yard and a 200 Amp service panel.   This stunning home resides in the award winning Banning Lewis Ranch community that features numerous schools, access to community centers, pickel ball, tennis, dog park, equatic center, pools, and over 65 acres of parks, trails, recreational areas to explore. Throughout much of the Banning Lewis community, you will experience beautiful views of Pikes Peak and the Front Range!  Close to all amenities, shopping, reasonable distance to Military base(s), hospitals etc...
